title: The Fast and the Furious : domestic and global box office revenue 2019
summary: This grouped bar chart shows Box office gross in million USD on the Y-axis for 9 different Movies for 2 groups North America, and Worldwide that are presented on the X-axis.

Out of all 2 groups, Worldwide had the highest Box office gross in million USD for Movie Fast & Furious Presents: Hobbs & Shaw and Worldwide had the lowest Box office gross in million USD for Movie The Fast and the Furious: Tokyo Drift.

Movie Fast & Furious Presents: Hobbs & Shaw and The Fast and the Furious: Tokyo Drift had the biggest gap of 70519.0 between the highest and lowest Box office gross in million USD found for Worldwide.

Averaging all 2 groups North America, and Worldwide, the Movie Furious 7 is the maximum Box office gross in million USD and The Fast and the Furious: Tokyo Drift is the minimum Box office gross in million USD.
